{"title":"ASCII","uid":"f6a1e2002f17c9eaebd46f737b9ec1f3","slug":"hexo-filterasciinema","date":"2022-12-26T16:16:00.840Z","updated":"2022-12-22T18:37:36.770Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hexo-filterasciinema.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<script src=\"/assets/asciinema-player.js\"></script><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"/assets/asciinema-player.css\" /># hexo-filter-asciinema\n\n<p><a href=\"https://nodejs.org/en/\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/npm/v/npm.svg\" alt=\"npm\"></a><br><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/hexo-filter-asciinema\"><img src=\"https://badge.fury.io/js/hexo-filter-asciinema.svg\" alt=\"NPM version\"></a><br><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/hexo-filter-asciinema\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/npm/dt/hexo-filter-asciinema.svg\" alt=\"npm\"></a><br><a href=\"https://github.com/mythsman/hexo-filter-asciinema/blob/master/LICENSE\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/license/mythsman/hexo-filter-asciinema.svg\" alt=\"GitHub license\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://nodei.co/npm/hexo-filter-asciinema/\"><img src=\"https://nodei.co/npm/hexo-filter-asciinema.png\" alt=\"NPM\"></a></p>\n<h2 id=\"Desciption\"><a href=\"#Desciption\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Desciption\"></a>Desciption</h2><p>A simple plugin which can embed asciinema-player in your article with local file.</p>\n<p>Though the plugin <a href=\"https://github.com/narongdejsrn/hexo-tag-asciinema\">hexo-tag-asciinema</a> does a similar thing . That one relies on <code>asciinema.org</code> ,  while this one relies just on local file.</p>\n<h2 id=\"Configuration\"><a href=\"#Configuration\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Configuration\"></a>Configuration</h2><p>Add the following configuration in the _config.yml of your site.</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight yml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># hexo-filter-asciinema</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">asciinema:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">enable:</span> <span class=\"literal\">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"Usage\"><a href=\"#Usage\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Usage\"></a>Usage</h2><p>When you want to add asciicast.json in your article, just put the file in the right place and write like this:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[<span class=\"string\">@asciinema</span>](<span class=\"link\">path/to/asciicast.cast</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"Release\"><a href=\"#Release\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Release\"></a>Release</h2><h3 id=\"1-0-6\"><a href=\"#1-0-6\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.0.6\"></a>1.0.6</h3><ul>\n<li>upgrade asciinema.js to 3.0.0-rc.1.</li>\n<li>fix <code>window.wrap</code> error.</li>\n</ul>\n","text":"# hexo-filter-asciinema DesciptionA simple plugin which can embed asciinema-player in your article with local file. Though the plugin hexo-t...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":615,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Desciption\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Desciption</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Configuration\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Configuration</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Usage\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Usage</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Release\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Release</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-0-6\"><span class=\"toc-t